# Messaging System Enhancements (Sprint 4)

Enhance the WhatsApp messaging module with error handling, media support, read receipts, search, and bot handoff.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Search**: I will implement a search that looks through both patient names and message content.
> - **Bot Handoff**: Switching back to BOT mode will trigger an automated message to the user.
> - **Media**: Rendering support for Images, PDFs, and Audio will be added.

