- Update [getConversations](file:///c:/Users/Lenovo/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/klinikapp/backend/src/modules/messaging/messaging.service.ts#17-47) to support `search` query (name, phone, message content).
- Add `handleStatusUpdate` to update message status (DELIVERED, READ) and emit `message_status_updated` socket event.
